data.description: Nestled in the serene countryside, this charming farm-style house offers a tranquil escape with the allure of simplicity. Boasting three bedrooms and two baths, this home provides a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. The property has the added advantage of NO HOA, allowing for the freedom to personalize and enjoy the space to its fullest. The rear of the house is adorned with nature's beauty, as it seamlessly merges with the lush Army Corps forest that stretches to the shores of Lake Allatoona. A picturesque setting, where the soothing sounds of nature and the stunning views create a peaceful ambiance. The property invites a sense of connection with the outdoors, providing a serene retreat for those seeking a harmonious blend of countryside living and waterfront tranquility. Inside, the heart of the home is a welcoming open-concept living room, highlighted by a cozy fireplace that adds warmth and charm. Natural light floods the space, enhancing the inviting atmosphere. The recently constructed deck spans the entire length of the house, offering an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings, enjoying scenic views, and embracing the tranquil surroundings. This farm-style haven seamlessly combines modern comforts with the timeless appeal of a countryside retreat. Whether it's the inviting interior spaces, the proximity to the Army Corps forest, or the breathtaking vistas of Lake Allatoona, this property promises a lifestyle that celebrates the beauty of nature and the comforts of home.
